@startuml component-diagram
title Stock Guard - Component Diagram (Release 1.0)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Client tier" {
  [React SPA (Vite)] as Web
  note right of Web
    Login, Sidebar, role pages,
    inventory/usage modals, reports,
    settings, export (CSV/PDF where implemented).
  end note
}

package "Server tier" {
  [Express HTTP API] as Api
  [Route modules] as Routes
  note right of Routes
    /api/inventory, /api/users,
    /api/reports, /api/system-settings,
    /api/auth, /api/health, /api/logs
  end note
}

package "Data tier" {
  database "MongoDB" as DB
}
note right of DB
  Collections: users, inventories,
  usagelogs, systemsettings
  (Mongoose model names: User, etc.)
end note

[In-memory system log\n(server.js)] as Mem
note right of Mem
  GET /api/logs; optional filter;
  not persisted in MongoDB.
end note

Web -down-> Api : JSON over HTTP\n(REST, CORS)
Api -right-> Routes
Routes -down-> DB : Mongoose ODM
Api ..> Mem : append / read\nsystem events

@enduml
